🔍 *Validate Oracle Inventory*

To ensure consistency of information for GRID and each RDBMS HOME before patching, follow these steps as the oracle user:

1. *Switch to Oracle User:*
   
   su - oracle
   whoami # should be oracle
   

2. *Check GRID Home Inventory:*
   
   export ORACLE_HOME=/u01/grid/oracle/product/19/grid
   $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch lsinventory -detail
   

3. *Check Database Home Inventory:*
   
   export ORACLE_HOME=/u01/oracle/product/19/db
   $ORACLE_HOME/OPatch/opatch lsinventory -detail
   

4. *Verify Patch Descriptions:*
   
   /u01/app/oracle/product/19/db/OPatch/opatch lsinv | grep desc
   

This process will help ensure that your Oracle environments are correctly set up and ready for patching. ✅

