🔄 *Verify Instances Are Open and Accepting Connections* 🔄

Ensure that any instances that were started are open and accepting connections.

*Commands*:

export ORACLE_HOME=/u01/grid/oracle/product/19/grid
$ORACLE_HOME/bin/lsnrctl status

export ORACLE_HOME=/u01/oracle/product/19/db
export ORACLE_SID=<sid>
$ORACLE_HOME/bin/sqlplus / as sysdba
select * from v$instance;
select count(*), username from v$session group by username;

